WEBVTT

00:00:08.085 --> 00:00:10.825
(Lee Na Young)

00:00:16.695 --> 00:00:19.365
(Jung Eun Chae)

00:00:21.235 --> 00:00:23.635
(Lee Chung Ah)

00:00:31.105 --> 00:00:35.115
(Honour)

00:00:35.745 --> 00:00:38.385
(Supported by the Culture Ministry and Korea's Creative Content Agency)

00:00:39.015 --> 00:00:40.215
(All people, incidents, and backgrounds...)

00:00:40.285 --> 00:00:41.514
(in this drama are fictitious and unrelated to reality.)

00:00:41.515 --> 00:00:42.755
(Also, children and animals were filmed under production guidelines.)

00:00:43.385 --> 00:00:45.455
The defendant used a steel pipe...

00:00:46.025 --> 00:00:48.394
and caused the death of the victim, Park Je Yeol.

00:00:48.395 --> 00:00:49.625
While these facts are not in dispute,

00:00:49.825 --> 00:00:51.924
the question is whether the defendant's actions...

00:00:51.925 --> 00:00:53.995
fall under Article 21, Paragraph 1...

00:00:54.295 --> 00:00:56.765
of the Criminal Code as an act of self-defence.

00:00:58.165 --> 00:00:59.435
So, Seo Ji Yoon...

00:01:00.205 --> 00:01:01.375
was your sister.

00:01:03.335 --> 00:01:04.975
We were separated when we were kids.

00:01:06.605 --> 00:01:09.445
It wasn't until I went to college that I came to Korea to find her.

00:01:14.555 --> 00:01:15.955
My sister was in the hospital,

00:01:16.685 --> 00:01:18.125
but I was too late.

00:01:20.055 --> 00:01:22.095
Why I had to do what I did...

00:01:23.825 --> 00:01:25.265
Surely you understand, Shin Jae?

00:01:40.205 --> 00:01:41.875
When something happens to someone you love,

00:01:44.385 --> 00:01:46.685
your whole world comes crashing down.

00:01:47.685 --> 00:01:51.685
That vow, that resolve to make the world a different place.

00:01:52.785 --> 00:01:54.555
You know that as well as I do, Shin Jae.

00:01:56.055 --> 00:01:57.065
Verdict.

00:01:57.595 --> 00:01:59.025
Defendant Yoon Ra Young,

00:01:59.965 --> 00:02:00.965
not guilty.

00:02:04.605 --> 00:02:06.565
Ultimately, we want the same thing.

00:02:07.775 --> 00:02:11.205
A world with no more victims like my sister or Attorney Yoon.

00:02:11.875 --> 00:02:15.415
And in the world we'll create, that's exactly what will happen.

00:02:20.555 --> 00:02:24.755
(The late Seo Ji Yoon)

00:02:30.025 --> 00:02:32.065
(Episode 11)

00:02:34.835 --> 00:02:36.365
You've been through so much.

00:02:37.205 --> 00:02:38.665
You're the ones who've been through a lot.

00:02:41.875 --> 00:02:42.905
Thanks, Jeong Woo.

00:02:45.375 --> 00:02:48.715
Prosecutors will appeal right away. We must prepare for the next trial.

00:02:49.345 --> 00:02:52.985
I know. But we've bought some time, so it doesn't matter.

00:02:53.915 --> 00:02:55.955
But where's Shin Jae?

00:03:03.625 --> 00:03:04.665
You're here?

00:03:05.895 --> 00:03:07.565
What's with the huge spread?

00:03:08.135 --> 00:03:09.135
Sit down.

00:03:09.765 --> 00:03:12.435
I felt like it's been a while since we've had a proper meal.

00:03:19.905 --> 00:03:20.915
Go on, eat.

00:03:21.845 --> 00:03:23.115
You look completely drained.

00:03:24.015 --> 00:03:25.015
Shin Jae.

00:03:26.545 --> 00:03:28.255
That video from the trial... What was it?

00:03:29.115 --> 00:03:32.555
Right, what was it? You said we'd talk when she got out.

00:03:32.625 --> 00:03:33.955
Let's eat first. We can talk after.

00:03:35.225 --> 00:03:36.225
That footage...

00:03:37.665 --> 00:03:39.495
Min Seo filmed it, didn't she?

00:03:41.135 --> 00:03:42.465
Where did you get that footage?

00:03:49.475 --> 00:03:51.545
You're right. Min Seo filmed it.

00:03:53.845 --> 00:03:55.745
You met Min Seo?

00:03:56.345 --> 00:03:59.045
You never said anything about that.

00:04:00.085 --> 00:04:02.555
Did you find her? Where is Min Seo now?

00:04:05.355 --> 00:04:07.255
She doesn't want to see you.

00:04:10.355 --> 00:04:12.825
I guess a nice meal is out of the question.

00:04:15.865 --> 00:04:17.435
LnJ is going to be dissolved.

00:04:18.165 --> 00:04:19.835
Haeil is already processing the dissolution.

00:04:22.405 --> 00:04:23.875
I was expecting that.

00:04:24.345 --> 00:04:26.705
Since Haeil is representing the perpetrators,

00:04:26.905 --> 00:04:29.475
it makes no sense for us to stay under them.

00:04:30.415 --> 00:04:34.315
Let's leave. We'll strike out on our own and face whatever comes.

00:04:34.715 --> 00:04:38.185
The three of us together can make anything work.

00:04:38.425 --> 00:04:39.625
I'm not going with you all.

00:04:42.995 --> 00:04:44.495
This is the end of LnJ.

00:04:46.365 --> 00:04:47.665
It's time for us to go our separate ways.

00:04:48.835 --> 00:04:50.665
What are you talking about?

00:04:50.935 --> 00:04:52.965
- Shin Jae. - In my heart,

00:04:54.205 --> 00:04:56.775
I think this was always going to be our final chapter.

00:04:58.075 --> 00:05:01.615
The moment we could finally put the past behind us.

00:05:03.415 --> 00:05:05.045
I wondered if that day would ever come,

00:05:06.185 --> 00:05:07.415
and now here it is.

00:05:08.655 --> 00:05:10.055
As for the Connect In case,

00:05:10.415 --> 00:05:12.825
you'll handle it just fine without me.

00:05:26.835 --> 00:05:28.635
You'll have to wait for the attorneys for that.

00:05:31.105 --> 00:05:32.345
It's all right, Ye Ji. Just let them.

00:05:33.075 --> 00:05:34.115
But, Attorney...

00:05:34.475 --> 00:05:36.445
It's fine. There's nothing we can do.

00:05:44.685 --> 00:05:46.255
Don't take it too hard.

00:05:48.825 --> 00:05:51.395
When you get down to it, you brought this on yourselves.

00:05:52.695 --> 00:05:55.495
I'll take back any employees who want to return to Haeil,

00:05:55.565 --> 00:05:56.965
so you needn't worry about that.

00:05:58.865 --> 00:06:00.265
And if you two want,

00:06:00.535 --> 00:06:02.035
we can find positions for you at Haeil too.

00:06:02.405 --> 00:06:05.605
No, thank you. We have no intention of staying with Haeil.

00:06:06.245 --> 00:06:08.515
We'll be leaving as soon as everything is settled.

00:06:10.075 --> 00:06:11.685
It's your choice.

00:06:12.515 --> 00:06:14.815
Then I guess you'll have to start from scratch.

00:06:15.585 --> 00:06:17.585
The Connect In case, without Haeil's help...

00:06:18.555 --> 00:06:19.755
Let's see how well you wrap that up.

00:06:36.075 --> 00:06:37.245
Hey, Kang Shin Jae!

00:06:39.345 --> 00:06:40.975
Kang Shin Jae, open up!

00:06:45.145 --> 00:06:47.855
Are you ignoring my calls? Are you really doing this to me?

00:06:50.015 --> 00:06:53.995
I know you're in there! I saw your car in the parking lot.

00:06:57.465 --> 00:06:58.665
Hey, Kang Shin Jae!

00:07:01.895 --> 00:07:03.935
Why I had to do what I did...

00:07:04.805 --> 00:07:06.305
Surely you understand, Shin Jae?

00:07:09.075 --> 00:07:10.775
Hey, why does everything have to be on your terms?

00:07:11.345 --> 00:07:12.905
You just say we're done, and that's it?

00:07:13.605 --> 00:07:15.875
Hey, you have to at least explain yourself!

00:07:16.345 --> 00:07:18.285
Ultimately, we want the same thing.

00:07:18.785 --> 00:07:22.215
A world with no more victims like my sister or Attorney Yoon.

00:07:23.885 --> 00:07:26.055
Are you really going to cut us off like this?

00:07:28.955 --> 00:07:30.865
Open the door, Kang Shin Jae!

00:07:33.195 --> 00:07:34.535
Hey, Kang Shin Jae!

00:07:35.165 --> 00:07:36.165
Shin Jae!

00:07:37.195 --> 00:07:38.635
Hey, Kang Shin Jae!

00:07:40.405 --> 00:07:41.405
(LnJ)

00:07:47.375 --> 00:07:48.375
(Thank you)

00:07:53.445 --> 00:07:55.285
Okay, I've put out the most urgent fire.

00:07:55.915 --> 00:07:58.625
I explained to Su Eun that we have to leave Haeil,

00:07:59.085 --> 00:08:01.295
and she said she'll let the other victims know.

00:08:02.655 --> 00:08:04.195
What is wrong with her?

00:08:05.025 --> 00:08:07.095
Seriously, what is up with Kang Shin Jae?

00:08:07.665 --> 00:08:09.694
- Did you see Shin Jae? - See her?

00:08:09.695 --> 00:08:11.035
I didn't even get a glimpse of her.

00:08:11.365 --> 00:08:13.835
You're just like her. I was so worried about you then,

00:08:13.905 --> 00:08:15.505
and now I'm so frustrated I could explode.

00:08:15.975 --> 00:08:18.205
You two will be the death of me, I swear.

00:08:20.945 --> 00:08:23.075
Something's not right.

00:08:23.945 --> 00:08:24.985
What is?

00:08:25.485 --> 00:08:26.485
That video.

00:08:27.115 --> 00:08:29.685
There's no way Min Seo would've given that file to Shin Jae.

00:08:33.555 --> 00:08:35.255
There must be a reason for it.

00:08:35.695 --> 00:08:37.365
The way Shin Jae's suddenly acting like this,

00:08:37.665 --> 00:08:38.995
Min Seo and that video...

00:08:41.365 --> 00:08:44.005
We have to figure out what the reason is.

00:08:45.635 --> 00:08:49.405
Gosh, it's finally sinking in that we're on the same team now.

00:08:50.575 --> 00:08:53.175
So, what's the plan?

00:08:53.675 --> 00:08:55.215
Just as you wanted,

00:08:55.745 --> 00:08:57.415
Attorney Yoon got out safely,

00:08:58.085 --> 00:08:59.445
so now we move on to the next stage.

00:09:07.525 --> 00:09:10.125
This is the detonator that will blow up Haeil.

00:09:12.465 --> 00:09:15.735
Haeil is an accomplice, and the root of this cartel.

00:09:17.405 --> 00:09:18.865
(Submitting key evidence in the Seo Ji Yoon case)

00:09:23.905 --> 00:09:25.475
(I'm writing to reveal the truth about the wrongful death...)

00:09:26.745 --> 00:09:28.745
(of the late actress, Seo Ji Yoon.)

00:09:28.775 --> 00:09:29.875
And now, for our next story.

00:09:30.215 --> 00:09:32.444
The investigation into Seo Ji Yoon's sexual exploitation...

00:09:32.445 --> 00:09:34.715
has been effectively concluded with no charges filed.

00:09:34.985 --> 00:09:37.184
Prosecutors said her call logs, the key piece of evidence,

00:09:37.185 --> 00:09:39.385
were lost during the investigation.

00:09:39.585 --> 00:09:41.994
With insufficient evidence to prove the charges,

00:09:41.995 --> 00:09:44.525
all the influential figures under investigation...

00:09:44.595 --> 00:09:46.265
will not be indicted.

00:09:54.435 --> 00:09:56.605
(Haeil Law Firm)

00:09:56.675 --> 00:09:58.675
For the last 20 years,

00:09:59.145 --> 00:10:02.575
the reason they kept getting away with the same crimes but new names,

00:10:03.375 --> 00:10:05.485
is because they believed they would never be punished.

00:10:06.045 --> 00:10:09.655
Because behind the scenes, Haeil was pulling strings for them.

00:10:10.985 --> 00:10:13.985
Unless Haeil is gone for good, things will go back to the old ways.

00:10:15.225 --> 00:10:17.525
So this is why I was part of your plan.

00:10:18.225 --> 00:10:20.095
Because if I'm the one to expose this,

00:10:20.765 --> 00:10:22.335
it'll have the biggest impact.

00:10:27.335 --> 00:10:28.375
Can you go through with it?

00:10:28.905 --> 00:10:30.875
It means stabbing your own mother in the back.

00:10:33.805 --> 00:10:36.545
You once said Haeil was legacy code that needed to be deleted long ago.

00:10:37.275 --> 00:10:38.315
You were right.

00:10:39.345 --> 00:10:40.385
Dismantling Haeil...

00:10:41.015 --> 00:10:43.715
is what I agreed to the moment we decided to get in the same boat.

00:11:16.115 --> 00:11:17.185
Why did you do it?

00:11:17.925 --> 00:11:19.885
Why bring me into this world just to abandon me in the fiery pit?

00:11:22.925 --> 00:11:24.095
It's too late for that now.

00:11:24.595 --> 00:11:25.865
Because I've already settled the score.

00:11:29.735 --> 00:11:30.865
The Connect videos...

00:11:31.505 --> 00:11:32.605
I'm the one who uploaded them.

00:11:38.805 --> 00:11:40.945
I guess even the Almighty decided to send someone my way.

00:11:41.545 --> 00:11:42.645
Someone to help me.

00:11:43.215 --> 00:11:44.515
He's the one who told me...

00:11:45.115 --> 00:11:46.685
who my birth mother was.

00:11:50.555 --> 00:11:52.025
I've been thinking about it this whole time.

00:11:52.255 --> 00:11:55.095
I wondered if you would recognise me.

00:11:56.155 --> 00:11:57.495
They say blood calls to blood.

00:11:58.725 --> 00:12:00.295
"Could she really not know, right to the end?"

00:12:15.545 --> 00:12:17.985
(No posts)

00:12:18.045 --> 00:12:20.285
(Send message)

00:12:36.835 --> 00:12:38.435
Thank you for being so understanding.

00:12:39.265 --> 00:12:41.105
Just until I find a proper office,

00:12:41.475 --> 00:12:44.035
I'll be using the house like this for a bit.

00:12:44.545 --> 00:12:46.275
It's fine with me. Do whatever you need to.

00:12:47.475 --> 00:12:49.815
Any news about Min Seo?

00:12:50.545 --> 00:12:52.244
They said there's no record she's left the country...

00:12:52.245 --> 00:12:54.585
and no signs of activity yet.

00:12:55.585 --> 00:12:58.125
With a warrant out for her arrest, it can't be easy for her to hide.

00:13:00.355 --> 00:13:02.395
I can't rest easy until we find her.

00:13:02.925 --> 00:13:07.165
A junior is keeping me updated, so try not to worry too much.

00:13:08.965 --> 00:13:09.965
Okay.

00:13:19.975 --> 00:13:22.975
About that conversation we had...

00:13:25.085 --> 00:13:26.215
Our divorce.

00:13:28.215 --> 00:13:29.985
Have you thought about the settlement terms?

00:13:35.425 --> 00:13:37.495
Just tell me what you want.

00:13:38.025 --> 00:13:39.365
I'll agree to whatever you want.

00:13:41.235 --> 00:13:42.235
Hyun Jin.

00:13:43.895 --> 00:13:45.535
Do you really think...

00:13:46.335 --> 00:13:47.735
that's the only option...

00:13:48.535 --> 00:13:49.605
we have left?

00:13:58.345 --> 00:13:59.345
You have never...

00:14:00.345 --> 00:14:01.655
asked me...

00:14:03.185 --> 00:14:04.825
to stay, not even once.

00:14:07.025 --> 00:14:11.625
Never mind who forgives who, or who's to blame.

00:14:12.065 --> 00:14:13.595
Just ask me to stay with you...

00:14:14.665 --> 00:14:16.265
and tell me you need me.

00:14:17.335 --> 00:14:19.635
Without a second thought, just like that.

00:14:20.265 --> 00:14:22.605
You've never once asked me to stay.

00:14:25.745 --> 00:14:28.945
That was all I ever wanted from you.

00:14:30.415 --> 00:14:32.615
Actually, about the divorce...

00:14:34.045 --> 00:14:36.315
I came here hoping we could reconsider.

00:14:37.215 --> 00:14:38.285
But...

00:14:39.155 --> 00:14:40.185
when it comes to marriage...

00:14:42.095 --> 00:14:43.095
You're right.

00:14:43.995 --> 00:14:46.465
It can't work if only one person wants it to.

00:14:49.295 --> 00:14:51.265
I'll have the papers sent over once they're ready.

00:14:51.805 --> 00:14:52.905
I should get going.

00:15:06.415 --> 00:15:10.015
(Haeil Law Firm)

00:15:10.315 --> 00:15:11.355
(Full adoption consent form)

00:15:11.385 --> 00:15:12.385
(Adoption Consent Adoptee: Lee Ji Yoon)

00:15:12.455 --> 00:15:14.395
(Birth mother, Lee Myeong Ja: Consent given)

00:15:16.025 --> 00:15:19.165
(Lee Tae Joo)

00:15:19.225 --> 00:15:21.695
(Fun field day)

00:15:23.135 --> 00:15:24.605
(CEO Seong Tae Im)

00:15:24.965 --> 00:15:25.965
So what?

00:15:26.505 --> 00:15:28.435
So what if Seo Ji Yoon is CEO Baek's sister?

00:15:28.835 --> 00:15:30.135
Twenty years ago,

00:15:30.935 --> 00:15:32.975
the people on the Seo Ji Yoon list...

00:15:33.145 --> 00:15:35.945
were targeted again on the Connect In list.

00:15:36.415 --> 00:15:39.585
And it all happened right as Baek Tae Joo approached us.

00:15:40.785 --> 00:15:42.015
And that same Baek Tae Joo...

00:15:42.415 --> 00:15:44.355
is the younger brother of the late Seo Ji Yoon.

00:15:45.685 --> 00:15:47.455
This can't be a coincidence.

00:15:47.955 --> 00:15:50.355
Because it isn't a coincidence. It was inevitable.

00:15:51.925 --> 00:15:53.225
CEO Baek Tae Joo...

00:15:53.865 --> 00:15:55.195
is the one who created Connect In.

00:15:56.995 --> 00:15:58.035
You understand...

00:15:59.265 --> 00:16:00.705
what his goal is now, don't you, Mom?

00:16:03.205 --> 00:16:04.875
What, was he trying to get revenge?

00:16:06.245 --> 00:16:07.545
How unfortunate for him.

00:16:08.015 --> 00:16:10.045
If something that pathetic could shake me,

00:16:10.315 --> 00:16:12.245
I never would have built all this in the first place.

00:16:12.885 --> 00:16:14.115
This is the real issue.

00:16:22.595 --> 00:16:24.225
I've sent the files regarding the National Assembly.

00:16:24.765 --> 00:16:27.365
We're counting on Haeil for the lobbying on this policy.

00:16:27.495 --> 00:16:30.535
I pulled some strings to wrap up the internal investigation.

00:16:31.665 --> 00:16:35.675
Relax. The Yeong development case will be overturned on final appeal.

00:16:36.105 --> 00:16:38.245
That side owes Haeil a few favours.

00:16:38.475 --> 00:16:40.175
There are dozens more files just like these.

00:16:40.605 --> 00:16:42.015
And that's just the ones involving Haeil.

00:16:45.085 --> 00:16:46.115
Don't tell me...

00:16:46.545 --> 00:16:49.285
you're not going to take down Haeil yourself, are you?

00:16:49.785 --> 00:16:51.625
I already gave them to the Corruption Investigation Office.

00:16:56.055 --> 00:16:57.865
You won't be able to interfere this time, Mom.

00:16:58.395 --> 00:17:00.825
Because I also sent the files on the users' personal corruption.

00:17:01.935 --> 00:17:04.605
Haeil, the users' shield, will fall.

00:17:04.805 --> 00:17:07.235
And the users who protected Haeil will go down with it.

00:17:07.975 --> 00:17:09.105
Without mutual destruction,

00:17:09.905 --> 00:17:11.345
I realised there was no other way to end this.

00:17:12.075 --> 00:17:13.905
And in the end, the world will discover...

00:17:14.745 --> 00:17:17.275
that this whole connection started with the Seo Ji Yoon case.

00:17:17.515 --> 00:17:21.185
Why on earth are you going this far?

00:17:21.915 --> 00:17:22.915
Mom.

00:17:23.655 --> 00:17:26.785
When I was little, I wanted to be just like you.

00:17:28.325 --> 00:17:30.295
Your attorney's pin...

00:17:31.125 --> 00:17:33.125
was as cool as a sheriff's badge to me.

00:17:34.535 --> 00:17:35.935
But as I grew up, I realised...

00:17:36.835 --> 00:17:40.265
that your badge didn't protect the powerless and the wronged,

00:17:40.805 --> 00:17:42.775
but those who just wanted to have more.

00:17:45.145 --> 00:17:46.675
(CEO Seong Tae Im)

00:17:47.675 --> 00:17:48.675
Maybe...

00:17:49.675 --> 00:17:53.115
my obsession with getting into LnJ was just a way of lying to myself.

00:17:54.185 --> 00:17:55.555
"I'm not like my mom."

00:17:56.555 --> 00:17:57.985
"I won't live my life like she does."

00:17:59.655 --> 00:18:00.685
But, Mom...

00:18:01.185 --> 00:18:02.295
I understand now.

00:18:02.995 --> 00:18:05.695
If I don't stop you, this will never end.

00:18:09.295 --> 00:18:10.465
You still don't get it, do you?

00:18:11.305 --> 00:18:15.075
How long will you see the world through rose-coloured glasses?

00:18:15.775 --> 00:18:17.175
That's not how it is, Shin Jae.

00:18:17.675 --> 00:18:20.045
The ground beneath your feet is a minefield,

00:18:20.505 --> 00:18:22.975
and to survive, you have to use every trick in the book...

00:18:23.515 --> 00:18:27.185
just to take a single step forward. Just like I had to.

00:18:27.845 --> 00:18:28.855
You're right, Mom.

00:18:29.455 --> 00:18:31.325
Maybe the world is a minefield.

00:18:31.855 --> 00:18:33.785
Unreasonable and absurd.

00:18:34.355 --> 00:18:35.555
But even so,

00:18:36.195 --> 00:18:38.295
I wanted to plant flowers in that minefield.

00:18:38.595 --> 00:18:40.365
Using every means at my disposal.

00:18:46.765 --> 00:18:48.035
And so, in the end,

00:18:48.575 --> 00:18:51.675
I found no other answer than to sacrifice myself.

00:18:53.445 --> 00:18:55.215
Because other than to jump into the fire,

00:18:57.415 --> 00:18:58.715
I had no other path.

00:19:01.655 --> 00:19:04.885
- Canada? - Things have been chaotic.

00:19:06.725 --> 00:19:09.895
Here. I found this in Park Je Yeol's car.

00:19:10.525 --> 00:19:12.195
I took a look. It'll be helpful.

00:19:12.865 --> 00:19:16.135
It'll ensure the Connect culprits rot in prison for a long time.

00:19:20.105 --> 00:19:21.105
Thank you.

00:19:21.905 --> 00:19:23.735
I won't let a single one of them get away.

00:19:24.205 --> 00:19:25.205
I promise.

00:19:28.115 --> 00:19:29.115
(VIP Networking, VIP Risk Management)

00:19:29.215 --> 00:19:30.215
(Complaint Handling, Expense Settlement)

00:19:30.645 --> 00:19:32.615
So meticulously organised.

00:19:36.315 --> 00:19:37.385
What is this?

00:19:39.555 --> 00:19:40.985
It's interesting, I'll admit.

00:19:41.795 --> 00:19:45.025
But what can I do with this system you've created?

00:19:46.025 --> 00:19:48.135
It's not about what you can do.

00:19:48.395 --> 00:19:51.935
First, think about what the people you want to get in with really want.

00:19:52.465 --> 00:19:55.875
You mean what people with money and power want?

00:19:56.535 --> 00:19:58.875
Using a system that's both thorough and discreet,

00:19:59.145 --> 00:20:01.845
what do you think people who have it all want to enjoy?

00:20:02.175 --> 00:20:03.745
If you were guaranteed to never get caught...

00:20:04.115 --> 00:20:07.515
and could get away with anything. Think about it carefully.

00:20:08.255 --> 00:20:11.555
He's trying to rope Park Je Yeol into something, isn't he?

00:20:12.085 --> 00:20:13.924
Laying the groundwork for him to commit crimes...

00:20:13.925 --> 00:20:14.925
with the app he's selling.

00:20:16.595 --> 00:20:19.295
The Connect In developer purposely approached Park Je Yeol.

00:20:20.165 --> 00:20:22.395
Encouraging him to misuse the app for illegal purposes.

00:20:28.005 --> 00:20:29.135
Don't you think it could be him?

00:20:30.475 --> 00:20:32.305
The one pulling Min Seo's strings.

00:20:33.645 --> 00:20:35.075
First, we need to find the developer.

00:20:35.845 --> 00:20:38.815
He must have left a trace somewhere in the app, like a fingerprint.

00:20:45.255 --> 00:20:46.255
Why?

00:20:46.325 --> 00:20:48.425
This is the admin app from Park Je Yeol's phone, right?

00:20:48.855 --> 00:20:51.225
This app was built using only open-source libraries.

00:20:51.295 --> 00:20:53.325
So that makes it hard to trace who made it.

00:20:59.705 --> 00:21:01.005
(Lee Myeong Hyeon, Social Affairs, Donglim Daily)

00:21:05.675 --> 00:21:08.545
The Corruption Investigation Office for High-ranking Officials...

00:21:08.615 --> 00:21:10.715
has begun a major investigation into those on the Connect In list.

00:21:11.015 --> 00:21:14.145
On charges of a systematic cover-up of their illegal activities,

00:21:14.485 --> 00:21:17.755
Seong Tae Im, the CEO of Haeil, the country's largest law firm,

00:21:17.915 --> 00:21:19.854
and its exec board were summoned.

00:21:19.855 --> 00:21:21.955
The trigger was the tip from the CEO's daughter,

00:21:22.025 --> 00:21:25.865
Attorney Kang at Haeil, who became a key whistleblower.

00:21:26.065 --> 00:21:29.495
The evidence covers a major incident that shook the nation 20 years ago,

00:21:29.695 --> 00:21:31.235
regarding the Seo Ji Yoon List incident.

00:21:31.505 --> 00:21:35.305
It contains key proof that Haeil systematically covered it up,

00:21:35.605 --> 00:21:37.274
which is set to send shockwaves.

00:21:37.275 --> 00:21:38.445
I heard she's on her way out.

00:21:40.205 --> 00:21:41.205
When is she coming out?

00:21:41.575 --> 00:21:42.575
Are you sure?

00:21:42.915 --> 00:21:44.645
- They say it's all clear. - She's coming.

00:21:44.715 --> 00:21:47.185
- But the car... She's coming out! - She's coming out.

00:21:52.755 --> 00:21:53.885
Ma'am, just a moment.

00:21:55.025 --> 00:21:56.295
Please, just give me a minute of your time.

00:22:01.125 --> 00:22:03.635
You know, don't you? Why Shin Jae is acting this way.

00:22:04.835 --> 00:22:06.765
I'm sure you know Shin Jae better than I do,

00:22:07.465 --> 00:22:08.705
but this isn't like her.

00:22:09.605 --> 00:22:11.135
Something's happened to Shin Jae, hasn't it?

00:22:11.305 --> 00:22:13.004
(Haeil Law Firm)

00:22:13.005 --> 00:22:15.075
She said, aside from jumping into the flames,

00:22:15.615 --> 00:22:17.175
there was no other path for her.

00:22:18.315 --> 00:22:19.445
And here we are.

00:22:21.815 --> 00:22:24.555
My daughter is a victim of Connect In.

00:22:26.355 --> 00:22:28.225
And someone is pulling her strings.

00:22:28.525 --> 00:22:31.225
I'm sure whatever Shin Jae is doing is connected.

00:22:32.165 --> 00:22:33.195
Please, help me.

00:22:40.165 --> 00:22:41.205
It's Baek Tae Joo.

00:22:45.645 --> 00:22:47.375
He's the one who pushed my daughter into the fire.

00:23:13.165 --> 00:23:15.305
We should have had this talk much sooner.

00:23:16.205 --> 00:23:18.945
I feel this conversation is a bit overdue.

00:23:20.245 --> 00:23:23.875
I never really thought of our relationship that way.

00:23:27.245 --> 00:23:29.315
Perhaps we can be, moving forward.

00:23:34.585 --> 00:23:35.595
As you well know,

00:23:36.055 --> 00:23:37.855
you can't get very far when you have too many enemies.

00:23:38.465 --> 00:23:42.465
But those who realise an enemy can become an ally tend to last longer.

00:23:46.235 --> 00:23:48.135
So, what is it you want?

00:23:48.735 --> 00:23:50.435
I was hoping we could let bygones be bygones...

00:23:50.875 --> 00:23:52.345
and work for our mutual benefit.

00:23:52.945 --> 00:23:54.875
I think it would be in both our interests.

00:23:55.915 --> 00:23:56.915
Mutual benefit?

00:23:58.075 --> 00:23:59.685
And what is it you want from me?

00:24:00.685 --> 00:24:03.685
Did you turn my file over to the Corruption Investigation Office too?

00:24:06.025 --> 00:24:07.025
And what if I didn't?

00:24:07.925 --> 00:24:09.625
What is it that you want, CEO Baek?

00:24:09.995 --> 00:24:11.495
Whatever I can give you, just say the word.

00:24:13.725 --> 00:24:14.995
You seem to think you still have...

00:24:15.865 --> 00:24:17.795
something to offer to me.

00:24:19.165 --> 00:24:21.835
Without Haeil, what could you possibly offer me?

00:24:22.605 --> 00:24:26.245
All you have left now is the "sex offender" label.

00:24:28.945 --> 00:24:32.015
So, what, you want me to die?

00:24:34.015 --> 00:24:35.185
Like your sister?

00:24:37.915 --> 00:24:40.724
I'm sorry that Seo Ji Yoon died.

00:24:40.725 --> 00:24:42.295
I never thought she'd do that.

00:24:46.295 --> 00:24:47.465
But doing this...

00:24:48.195 --> 00:24:50.395
won't bring your sister back to life.

00:25:40.515 --> 00:25:41.585
This was an enlightening conversation.

00:25:42.315 --> 00:25:45.885
Thank you for proving me right once again.

00:25:55.235 --> 00:25:56.235
It's a match.

00:25:57.895 --> 00:26:01.465
This was scraped from fragments of the Connect In app via forensics.

00:26:02.205 --> 00:26:04.735
And this code is from a security app CEO Baek made in the past.

00:26:06.545 --> 00:26:08.375
See? They're identical.

00:26:10.045 --> 00:26:13.445
He reused a past vulnerability to create the attack code.

00:26:13.745 --> 00:26:16.385
So, Baek Tae Joo created the Connect In app?

00:26:18.385 --> 00:26:22.225
(Baek Tae Joo)

00:26:23.425 --> 00:26:24.925
(Baek Tae Joo, Connect In App, Developer)

00:26:25.025 --> 00:26:26.725
He did all this...

00:26:27.625 --> 00:26:29.065
just to get his revenge?

00:26:30.095 --> 00:26:31.165
Then Shin Jae...

00:26:33.565 --> 00:26:37.175
knew all this and worked with him anyway.

00:27:29.695 --> 00:27:31.155
(Attorney Kang Shin Jae)

00:28:20.745 --> 00:28:21.745
Where's Han Min Seo?

00:28:23.115 --> 00:28:24.815
The daughter you abandoned, Attorney Yoon?

00:28:25.185 --> 00:28:27.685
I'm afraid you've come to the wrong person to find her.

00:28:28.085 --> 00:28:30.185
If anything at all happens to her,

00:28:30.685 --> 00:28:33.685
I will kill you with my bare hands.

00:28:35.125 --> 00:28:38.565
You make it sound like I put Han Min Seo up to this.

00:28:39.395 --> 00:28:41.125
Getting revenge on her parents...

00:28:41.565 --> 00:28:44.865
and posting those videos on Connect In were her own choices.

00:28:45.565 --> 00:28:46.905
Han Min Seo is an adult.

00:28:47.535 --> 00:28:51.204
She can make her own choices and be responsible. Don't you agree?

00:28:51.205 --> 00:28:52.275
Is that right?

00:28:52.575 --> 00:28:55.845
Would she have done it if she knew you created the Connect In app?

00:28:56.215 --> 00:28:59.515
All I did was create an app with a robust security system.

00:28:59.885 --> 00:29:02.285
Park Je Yeol and the users were the ones who abused it.

00:29:02.355 --> 00:29:04.315
But you knew it would be exploited.

00:29:04.555 --> 00:29:07.285
No, you built it so they would.

00:29:09.195 --> 00:29:10.355
And that's how I caught them all.

00:29:12.965 --> 00:29:15.295
Park Je Yeol, Haeil,

00:29:15.735 --> 00:29:19.205
and the vermin who kept getting away with these things.

00:29:21.335 --> 00:29:24.135
If I hadn't created Connect In, you think it wouldn't have happened?

00:29:25.575 --> 00:29:28.145
And if I hadn't, would you ever have caught them?

00:29:30.415 --> 00:29:33.845
That's why, in ten years, you all have changed nothing.

00:29:34.445 --> 00:29:37.385
Look. What happened to you...

00:29:37.885 --> 00:29:40.625
ended up happening to your daughter all over again.

00:29:43.795 --> 00:29:44.795
Right.

00:29:45.925 --> 00:29:49.795
But what happened to me also happened to your sister.

00:29:51.265 --> 00:29:53.565
Do you think this is...

00:29:54.435 --> 00:29:55.535
what your sister would have wanted?

00:30:12.385 --> 00:30:13.725
Han Min Seo will be safe.

00:30:14.385 --> 00:30:17.595
As long as you stay out of it, Attorney Yoon.

00:30:49.795 --> 00:30:51.725
Everything turned out just the way you wanted, Min Seo.

00:30:56.595 --> 00:30:57.635
CEO Baek?

00:31:02.505 --> 00:31:05.845
The people who tormented you are all going to pay the price now.

00:31:07.075 --> 00:31:09.445
This is what you wanted, isn't it?

00:31:13.115 --> 00:31:14.615
Where am I?

00:31:15.615 --> 00:31:17.085
Why am I here?

00:31:20.185 --> 00:31:22.795
The police are looking for you right now.

00:31:23.355 --> 00:31:25.565
Things got dangerous, so you're just laying low for a bit.

00:31:28.465 --> 00:31:30.335
Then what is this?

00:31:33.205 --> 00:31:35.975
Latvia, wasn't it? The place you said you wanted to go?

00:31:37.275 --> 00:31:40.675
You said you wanted a fresh start where nobody knows you.

00:31:44.115 --> 00:31:46.945
Hello? Over here! Is anyone there?

00:31:47.285 --> 00:31:50.255
- Help me! - Just rest until we get there.

00:31:52.525 --> 00:31:54.525
Everything will be peaceful very soon.

00:31:57.025 --> 00:31:58.025
Untie me, right now!

00:31:58.725 --> 00:31:59.725
I said, untie me!

00:32:00.725 --> 00:32:01.725
Sweet dreams.

00:32:03.865 --> 00:32:04.865
Untie me before you go!

00:32:07.565 --> 00:32:08.835
Hey, untie me!

00:32:28.025 --> 00:32:30.095
Yeouido and the government district are in complete chaos.

00:32:30.555 --> 00:32:32.094
Now the summonses have started,

00:32:32.095 --> 00:32:33.765
everyone is busy trying to save their skin.

00:32:34.025 --> 00:32:36.295
Statements are pouring in as they're all blaming each other.

00:32:37.435 --> 00:32:38.804
The fallout is so huge, it's very likely...

00:32:38.805 --> 00:32:40.065
they'll all be arrested and indicted.

00:32:40.735 --> 00:32:42.235
Haeil is going down with them,

00:32:42.975 --> 00:32:44.335
so they're not getting out of this one.

00:33:02.725 --> 00:33:05.625
The only hurdle we have left now is our Technology Demonstration.

00:33:07.495 --> 00:33:09.365
As long as we get a good score on the technical evaluation,

00:33:10.335 --> 00:33:12.205
we should be able to win the bid without any trouble.

00:33:26.215 --> 00:33:27.245
It's a perfect fit.

00:33:30.285 --> 00:33:31.785
Starting with this project,

00:33:32.525 --> 00:33:34.155
we're now sharing the same dream.

00:33:47.665 --> 00:33:49.905
If I were you, I'd make them all pay.

00:33:50.635 --> 00:33:52.905
You have every right to bring them to justice, Min Seo.

00:33:53.645 --> 00:33:56.745
And I know exactly how.

00:33:57.345 --> 00:33:59.645
I can even help you, if you want.

00:34:00.685 --> 00:34:03.385
So, feeling better now?

00:34:03.785 --> 00:34:07.025
The people who tormented you are all going to pay the price now.

00:34:07.485 --> 00:34:09.825
This is what you wanted, isn't it?

00:35:39.315 --> 00:35:42.115
(Bukgwang Hospital)

00:35:45.455 --> 00:35:46.455
(Han Min Seo)

00:36:25.865 --> 00:36:26.995
Where's my phone?

00:36:28.365 --> 00:36:29.995
It's in the patient belongings room.

00:36:33.335 --> 00:36:34.335
Take me there.

00:36:43.345 --> 00:36:45.945
Hey, I thought your shift was over.

00:36:46.345 --> 00:36:49.115
Yes. I was just about to head out.

00:36:49.655 --> 00:36:51.585
- Get home safe. - Okay.

00:36:59.695 --> 00:37:00.695
Here you go.

00:37:04.465 --> 00:37:05.465
What about my necklace?

00:37:05.735 --> 00:37:06.735
Your necklace?

00:37:11.975 --> 00:37:12.975
There wasn't one in here.

00:37:13.845 --> 00:37:14.945
(New message from Yoon Ra Young)

00:37:15.745 --> 00:37:17.115
(New message from Yoon Ra Young)

00:37:17.475 --> 00:37:19.015
By the way, about your shift tomorrow...

00:37:22.515 --> 00:37:24.085
Patient Han Min Seo has escaped her room.

00:37:34.695 --> 00:37:36.465
He's holding Min Seo hostage.

00:37:37.395 --> 00:37:39.965
So even if we find out who he is, there's nothing we can do.

00:37:42.375 --> 00:37:45.505
Then how did Shin Jae get the video Min Seo shot?

00:37:46.805 --> 00:37:48.505
Don't you think we should talk to Shin Jae?

00:37:53.185 --> 00:37:54.515
(Han Min Seo)

00:37:58.515 --> 00:37:59.525
Hello?

00:38:03.555 --> 00:38:04.555
Min Seo?

00:38:12.565 --> 00:38:13.565
Where are you right now?

00:38:21.275 --> 00:38:24.245
Seon Kyu, Min Seo just called.

00:38:25.215 --> 00:38:28.245
Yes, sir. We're looking for her now.

00:38:28.745 --> 00:38:31.385
She's at the hospital, so we'll ensure she is found safely.

00:38:31.455 --> 00:38:34.125
No. Just take care of her.

00:38:40.595 --> 00:38:44.165
(Death certificate)

00:38:44.795 --> 00:38:45.935
(Kim Cheol Gi, Director, Bukgwang Hospital)

00:38:46.005 --> 00:38:49.175
(Hospital Director: Im Seo Jin)

00:38:50.135 --> 00:38:52.975
(Record book)

00:38:53.375 --> 00:38:55.475
(Death certificate)

00:38:58.315 --> 00:38:59.385
(Cause of Death: Cardiopulmonary Arrest)

00:38:59.585 --> 00:39:00.985
(Han Ji Yeon)

00:39:51.795 --> 00:39:52.805
(Administration office)

00:39:55.065 --> 00:39:59.175
I'm sorry, but we have no patient by that name registered here.

00:40:02.775 --> 00:40:05.175
This is her. Are you sure you've never seen her?

00:40:05.715 --> 00:40:08.315
I'm sorry. We have no such patient.

00:40:09.145 --> 00:40:11.285
We traced her phone's last signal here.

00:40:11.315 --> 00:40:13.925
Look, she made a call from this location two hours ago.

00:40:14.055 --> 00:40:16.495
A cell tower's signal has a wide radius.

00:40:16.925 --> 00:40:18.555
Couldn't she have made the call from somewhere else?

00:40:19.925 --> 00:40:22.565
This was the only occupied building in this area.

00:40:23.195 --> 00:40:26.365
Or what? Are you saying she called from a mountain with no reception?

00:40:26.435 --> 00:40:28.765
I'm sorry, but there's nothing more I can tell you.

00:40:32.405 --> 00:40:34.605
Fine. I get it.

00:40:42.085 --> 00:40:44.385
(Han Ji Yeon)

00:40:45.955 --> 00:40:47.585
Ma'am, you're not allowed to touch that.

00:40:50.455 --> 00:40:52.665
(Death certificate: Han Ji Yeon)

00:40:59.535 --> 00:41:01.405
(Bukgwang Hospital)

00:41:08.975 --> 00:41:10.245
What did you find out?

00:41:10.345 --> 00:41:13.445
They insist it's not her chart and claim they've never seen her.

00:41:13.545 --> 00:41:14.945
That makes no sense.

00:41:15.245 --> 00:41:19.115
Then why is Min Seo's picture on it? And we know her phone pinged here.

00:41:19.255 --> 00:41:22.055
We can't press them any further without a warrant.

00:41:22.525 --> 00:41:23.625
And we can't search the premises either.

00:41:25.095 --> 00:41:26.365
Looks like the local precinct is here.

00:41:27.495 --> 00:41:28.495
Hello.

00:41:35.935 --> 00:41:37.435
Han Min Seo will be safe.

00:41:37.705 --> 00:41:40.945
As long as you stay out of it, Attorney Yoon.

00:41:46.315 --> 00:41:47.315
Baek Tae Joo.

00:41:51.085 --> 00:41:52.085
Ra Young.

00:41:52.725 --> 00:41:54.855
The prime suspect in a murder case, Ms. Han,

00:41:54.985 --> 00:41:58.625
has reportedly been found hiding out at a remote psychiatric hospital,

00:41:58.825 --> 00:42:00.425
prompting police to launch an urgent investigation.

00:42:00.725 --> 00:42:02.294
The hospital claims it has no record...

00:42:02.295 --> 00:42:03.865
of the patient ever being admitted...

00:42:03.965 --> 00:42:05.695
and is flatly denying the allegations,

00:42:05.765 --> 00:42:07.435
complicating the investigation.

00:42:07.535 --> 00:42:09.674
The hospital was also investigated in the past...

00:42:09.675 --> 00:42:11.404
after several patients died...

00:42:11.405 --> 00:42:13.705
under suspicious circumstances, including medication overdoses.

00:42:13.805 --> 00:42:17.945
This revelation increased suspicion surrounding the hospital.

00:42:32.865 --> 00:42:34.565
Something's happened to Min Seo.

00:42:35.265 --> 00:42:38.135
Something terrible might've happened to her.

00:42:39.165 --> 00:42:40.365
I just saw the news.

00:42:43.235 --> 00:42:46.475
Who do you think locked her up in there?

00:42:49.245 --> 00:42:52.075
It's Baek Tae Joo. He's the one who created Connect In.

00:42:57.555 --> 00:43:00.385
Don't tell me... Did you know?

00:43:02.385 --> 00:43:03.395
I did.

00:43:05.095 --> 00:43:08.965
Then how could you not say a single word to me?

00:43:09.865 --> 00:43:13.065
She might be safer in there, you know.

00:43:14.505 --> 00:43:16.405
Who knows what dangerous stunt she'd pull otherwise?

00:43:16.975 --> 00:43:19.204
It's no coincidence that all of us, Park Je Yeol, and Min Seo,

00:43:19.205 --> 00:43:21.445
got tangled up with Connect In.

00:43:21.805 --> 00:43:25.615
Even before Yoo Jeong came to us, before Park Je Yeol ran Connect In,

00:43:25.715 --> 00:43:28.215
we were already a part of his plan.

00:43:28.785 --> 00:43:31.455
He planned everything, even selling Min Seo to Connect In.

00:43:32.655 --> 00:43:35.685
And it's my fault he put Min Seo in that hospital.

00:43:38.095 --> 00:43:39.095
So?

00:43:41.595 --> 00:43:42.725
What do you mean, "So?"

00:43:43.435 --> 00:43:45.965
Min Seo could be dead because of Baek Tae Joo.

00:43:46.035 --> 00:43:48.835
But you said they haven't found her yet, right?

00:43:49.205 --> 00:43:51.235
She might've just walked out on her own.

00:43:51.935 --> 00:43:54.975
There's no proof CEO Baek was involved.

00:43:57.915 --> 00:43:58.975
Are you serious?

00:44:00.545 --> 00:44:01.545
I am.

00:44:08.285 --> 00:44:09.795
I never would have imagined...

00:44:11.055 --> 00:44:12.055
that I...

00:44:13.425 --> 00:44:14.925
would lose you like this.

00:44:56.305 --> 00:44:58.035
It's me. You can open up.

00:45:19.095 --> 00:45:22.125
If you want to see for yourself, open your mother's safe.

00:45:22.725 --> 00:45:25.195
You'll find out why Haeil has to disappear.

00:45:29.135 --> 00:45:30.475
And one more thing.

00:45:31.335 --> 00:45:33.545
And just in case you were worried,

00:45:34.205 --> 00:45:36.445
I'm taking very good care of Han Min Seo.

00:45:38.615 --> 00:45:40.285
If saving Ra Young is the price,

00:45:43.955 --> 00:45:44.955
then fine.

00:45:46.115 --> 00:45:47.785
I'll go to the fiery pit.

00:45:48.425 --> 00:45:49.425
Gladly.

00:45:49.925 --> 00:45:53.325
It wasn't until I went to college that I came to Korea to find her.

00:45:54.125 --> 00:45:55.565
My sister was in the hospital.

00:45:56.535 --> 00:45:58.965
Find out which hospital Seo Ji Yoon was admitted to.

00:46:11.275 --> 00:46:12.475
You are...

00:46:33.405 --> 00:46:34.965
I brought you some essentials.

00:46:36.475 --> 00:46:40.475
Do I have to hide that I'm safe from Attorney Yoon too?

00:46:42.405 --> 00:46:43.415
Yes.

00:46:43.975 --> 00:46:48.045
Otherwise, CEO Baek will find out, and he'll come after you.

00:46:48.415 --> 00:46:50.415
You're Ra Young's biggest weakness,

00:46:50.885 --> 00:46:54.725
and you're his weakness too since you know everything he's done.

00:46:55.985 --> 00:46:57.225
This will all be over in two days.

00:46:58.655 --> 00:47:00.195
Just stay here until the day of the tech demo.

00:47:02.425 --> 00:47:03.935
Why did you save me?

00:47:04.235 --> 00:47:06.035
You could've just looked the other way.

00:47:13.605 --> 00:47:17.245
You saw the newborn's jacket that Ra Young has, right?

00:47:18.575 --> 00:47:21.585
This isn't your fault, Min Seo. I'll handle this.

00:47:24.585 --> 00:47:25.755
Because I'm the one who bought it.

00:47:55.615 --> 00:47:56.615
(Yoon Ra Young)

00:47:58.715 --> 00:47:59.725
Min Seo.

00:48:00.385 --> 00:48:04.795
There's so much I want to ask, where you are and if you're okay.

00:48:05.595 --> 00:48:09.395
But I just need you to remember one thing.

00:48:10.395 --> 00:48:15.365
No matter how much you may hate me or whatever you may have done,

00:48:16.005 --> 00:48:17.405
know that I'm here for you,

00:48:18.475 --> 00:48:21.245
and that I'm not going anywhere.

00:48:28.885 --> 00:48:30.385
I'm very sorry, sir.

00:48:31.685 --> 00:48:34.585
I have no idea how she just vanished from the hospital without a trace.

00:48:35.525 --> 00:48:37.355
And the police investigation is giving me such a headache.

00:48:38.295 --> 00:48:42.095
A complicated investigation won't do you any good, sir, so...

00:48:42.725 --> 00:48:46.235
- can you wait till it dies down... - Wait.

00:48:58.145 --> 00:48:59.475
(137S 5779)

00:49:01.345 --> 00:49:03.885
So, the reason you haven't caught Han Min Seo...

00:49:04.815 --> 00:49:05.815
was right here.

00:49:06.455 --> 00:49:08.425
(137S 5779)

00:49:14.525 --> 00:49:15.525
(Smart City OS Technology Demonstration)

00:49:29.915 --> 00:49:30.915
Sign here, please.

00:49:36.685 --> 00:49:37.815
(CCTV bypass secured. Server access granted.)

00:49:40.485 --> 00:49:43.855
(Smart City OS Technology Demonstration)

00:50:45.085 --> 00:50:46.285
Okay, I'm in.

00:50:49.155 --> 00:50:50.595
Authentication successful.

00:50:58.435 --> 00:50:59.595
I put the cameras on a 20-minute loop.

00:51:00.005 --> 00:51:01.135
You have to be out before then.

00:51:01.735 --> 00:51:02.735
Got it.

00:51:03.735 --> 00:51:04.975
Authentication successful.

00:51:40.975 --> 00:51:41.975
You're connected.

00:51:42.945 --> 00:51:46.415
Hey, I've already taken care of the firmware for your sensor.

00:51:47.385 --> 00:51:48.385
(Admin biometric authentication required)

00:52:10.835 --> 00:52:12.635
(Admin biometric authentication required)

00:52:14.445 --> 00:52:16.405
There. I'm implanting the installation code now.

00:52:17.745 --> 00:52:19.515
Now, as long as the demonstration goes off without a hitch,

00:52:20.015 --> 00:52:22.215
the whole world will find out who Baek Tae Joo really is.

00:52:24.585 --> 00:52:27.525
Because of the security network, it needs external authentication.

00:52:27.625 --> 00:52:30.325
That way, if Baek Tae Joo snoops around, he'll never find it.

00:52:30.625 --> 00:52:33.095
It will activate tomorrow when you enter the code.

00:52:33.395 --> 00:52:34.395
All done.

00:52:37.665 --> 00:52:38.935
(Security alert: Main server access)

00:52:39.065 --> 00:52:40.465
(Admin biometric authentication approved)

00:52:41.765 --> 00:52:46.035
Good. Baek Tae Joo must know by now. You need to leave right now.

00:52:46.375 --> 00:52:48.845
But are you sure you'll be okay?

00:52:49.405 --> 00:52:51.245
Don't worry about me. Just go.

00:52:59.355 --> 00:53:02.025
(User: Kang Shin Jae, Legal Team)

00:53:23.305 --> 00:53:25.115
I appreciate your help. So this is it.

00:53:58.945 --> 00:54:00.345
(This is innovation. We design optimised IT strategies.)

00:54:12.795 --> 00:54:14.995
This is an apartment complex in Mujin.

00:54:16.465 --> 00:54:17.995
It appears we have an intruder.

00:54:19.265 --> 00:54:22.735
With a conventional system, the victim or a witness...

00:54:22.905 --> 00:54:26.375
would have to report the crime before police could be dispatched.

00:54:26.945 --> 00:54:28.775
But in a city run by The Prime, things are different.

00:54:29.175 --> 00:54:32.944
The Prime's OS analyses movement and behaviour patterns,

00:54:32.945 --> 00:54:34.985
identifying them as a threat within five seconds.

00:54:35.445 --> 00:54:38.615
This information is sent instantly to the police control center,

00:54:38.755 --> 00:54:40.985
and the closest security team is dispatched.

00:54:41.355 --> 00:54:42.685
Before a crime can even be committed,

00:54:43.455 --> 00:54:45.425
the threat is eliminated first.

00:54:46.195 --> 00:54:48.295
In the live demo that will follow shortly,

00:54:48.365 --> 00:54:50.995
we will show you this entire process in real time.

00:54:51.235 --> 00:54:55.705
You will see just how our algorithm perfectly protects Mujin residents,

00:54:55.905 --> 00:54:58.735
and you will witness it with your very own eyes.

00:55:03.815 --> 00:55:05.615
Thank you. After a short break,

00:55:05.715 --> 00:55:07.244
we will commence the QnA...

00:55:07.245 --> 00:55:09.415
and The Prime's Smart City Demonstration.

00:55:17.055 --> 00:55:18.425
Here to congratulate me?

00:55:19.295 --> 00:55:20.325
I told you, didn't I?

00:55:21.095 --> 00:55:24.965
If anything happens to Han Min Seo, I'll kill you with my own hands.

00:55:27.865 --> 00:55:30.735
We are one step away from a whole new world.

00:55:31.205 --> 00:55:32.974
Why must humans ruin everything...

00:55:32.975 --> 00:55:35.605
because they can't bear to shed the last drop of blood?

00:55:39.575 --> 00:55:40.715
Notice how Shin Jae isn't here?

00:55:42.815 --> 00:55:45.585
Aren't you curious where she might be right now?

00:56:02.905 --> 00:56:03.905
(Gaseous fire suppression system)

00:56:04.005 --> 00:56:06.975
Pressing this instantly releases a clean agent fire suppression gas.

00:56:09.175 --> 00:56:11.615
It will remove all the oxygen from the room Shin Jae is in,

00:56:11.975 --> 00:56:14.045
bringing it to zero percent within three minutes.

00:56:15.445 --> 00:56:19.655
I wonder how many minutes she can last without oxygen.

00:56:22.385 --> 00:56:23.795
If you don't want to find out,

00:56:32.535 --> 00:56:33.565
keep your mouth shut.

00:57:26.315 --> 00:57:30.225
(Honour)

00:58:18.775 --> 00:58:23.405
I don't understand why I had to go through all of this.

00:58:23.975 --> 00:58:26.415
You just left her with Baek Tae Joo?

00:58:26.775 --> 00:58:29.015
I don't call this surveillance. I call it protection.

00:58:29.215 --> 00:58:31.415
I'm telling you, this was the missing person's last location!

00:58:31.755 --> 00:58:34.185
Seon Kyu, can you hear me? Seon Kyu.

00:58:34.655 --> 00:58:38.755
- Was this your plan all along? - And you thought I'd let it slide?

00:58:39.625 --> 00:58:42.925
If you ask me, the most dangerous person in this hall right now...

00:58:42.995 --> 00:58:44.865
is you.